trans:
We have a nice customerbase within your own region. This way you will visit companies like, Defense, KFC, Animalpark Emmen or several big hospitality companies.
You're always in contact with your colleagues at the office;
There are plenty of possibilities within the company to grow which allows for continuous learning of new things, keeping the job challenging.
Job-requirements:
You completed a technical education;
You have a certificate for F gasses category 1;
You can show workexperience as a (independent) refrigeration technician;
You have good communication skills and a customer directed attitude;
You are representable, you're the namecard of the company;
You have your driverslicense B.
What do you get in return?
A challenging and diverse fulltime job with a lot of freedom;
